{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 64469, "create_time": 1648880402, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "cz上次去微软入职，背调表里面有是否是党员or预备党员一项，据hr说是一票否决", "timestamp": 1648880402}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 64476, "create_time": 1648880573, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "为了利益入党，现在又为了利益想退党又不敢退，我不喜欢CCP，但你们就这么把进入CCP的身体当玩具吗。", "timestamp": 1648880573}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 64478, "create_time": 1648880646, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: 同感，这种行为多少有点恶心了", "timestamp": 1648880646}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 64481, "create_time": 1648880964, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "可能会有影响，当具体影响有多大谁也说不准，有可能共和党上台政策会更极端", "timestamp": 1648880964}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 64483, "create_time": 1648881091, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "至于不转正会有什么影响的问题，你还是找学校有关部门问一下吧", "timestamp": 1648881091}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 64488, "create_time": 1648881529, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Bob: 人可以因为利益入党，也可以因为政治信仰入党，人可以因为利益出国，也可以因为学术追求出国。", "timestamp": 1648881529}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 64490, "create_time": 1648881574, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "如果下定决心移民美国，这边预备转正的事就先拖着或者拒了。如果还有回国的可能性的话，我奉劝你别退党，因为有政治污点的人在中国会有极多不便", "timestamp": 1648881574}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del":